#### Control scheme

Camera controls:  Move mouse

### List of known bugs/issues

* Opening Pause screen whilst on Start menu causes an issue where menu items cannot be selected.  
* Changing default controls is untested.  
* No controller support.   
* Music doesn’t stop in pause menu.  
* No “Game Over” message on player death
